flowchart TB
  subgraph SETUP["1) One-time setup in Claude"]
    A["Paste one command in Terminal"]
    B["Paste or upload your CV,<br/>then answer a few questions:<br/>roles, industries, location, salary"]
    C["Profile and preferences are saved"]
    A --> B --> C
  end

  subgraph MATCHING["2) Matching run"]
